Edit the file in tool and save the file
Go to github desktop to view the changes in the file.
If the changes are fine then update the commit description regarding the update and click Commit
This process is known as staging in which the changes are locally updated but not in github cloud
Click push origin.

It is a good practice to update the file from a draft branch rather than a main branch.
So before making updates you must create a draft branch of the main branch and make changes.
